OL,5, The mother of a black 13-year-old boy  
OL,6, says she feels "betrayed" after he was 
OL,7, surrounded by armed police when his    
OL,8, water pistol was mistaken for a gun.   
OL,10,FThe boy was "rammed" off his bike,     
OL,11,Fhandcuffed and confronted by marksmen  
OL,12,Fin Hackney, east London, in July.      
OL,14,FHis mother said: "I know - and the     
OL,15,Fpolice know - that they would not have 
OL,16,Ftreated my son in the way they did if  
OL,17,Fhe had been a white 13-year-old boy."  
OL,19,FThe Met Police's Det Ch Supt James     
OL,20,FConway apologised for "trauma" caused. 
